<topic id="cat-Time_Functions" revisionNumber="1" title="Time Functions">
  <developerConceptualDocument xmlns="http://ddue.schemas.microsoft.com/authoring/2003/5" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
    <section address="Section1">
      <title>Time Functions</title>
      <content>
        <table>
          <tableHeader>
            <row>
              <entry>
                <para>Assembly</para>
              </entry>
              <entry>
                <para>Function</para>
              </entry>
              <entry>
                <para>Description</para>
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tableHeader>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RDD</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RDD.Functions.AdsSetTime(System.IntPtr,System.UInt32,System.String,System.UInt16)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>查看 ADS 文档，了解更多关于此函数的信息。</para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.AmPm(System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将24小时制军用时间转换为12小时制时间。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.ConTime(System.UInt32,System.UInt32,System.UInt32)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      将表示小时、分钟和秒的一组数字格式化为时间字符串。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.ElapTime(System.String,System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      返回两个时间字符串之间的差值。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.FTime</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      返回由 FFCount()、FFirst() 或 FNext() 找到的文件的时间戳。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.VFP.Functions.FTime(System.String)</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      Returns the last modification time for a file.
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.RT</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.RT.Functions.GetTickCountLow</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
            Get the number of 1/10000 seconds that have elapsed since Windows was started.
            </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.GetTimeSep</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
      返回当前用于时间字符串的分隔字符。
    </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.Core</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
                <codeEntityReference qualifyHint="false" autoUpgrade="true">M:XSharp.Core.Functions.GetTimeZoneDiff</codeEntityReference>
              </para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
            Returns TimeZone difference for current timezone in Hours
            </para>
            </entry>
          </row>
          <row>
            <entry>
              <para>XSharp.VFP</para>
            </entry>
            <entry>
              <para>
